This paper is about semantic parsing, which is a subfield of natural language processing (NLP). The paper proposes a method for cross-domain semantic parsing, which involves adapting a semantic parser trained on one domain to another domain. This is a common problem in NLP, and is likely to be of interest to researchers in several subfields.
